snippet.title: Knights and Glory Game Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Google Play: http://bit.ly/KnightsGlory (Open Beta)
App Store: TestFlight (PM us via Facebook)


Knights and Glory is an online strategy card game with unique tactical battle simulation mechanics that focuses on the conflicts between medieval civilization around the world.

Official Page: http://playplayfun.com/knights-and-glory-game-official-page/
Facebook: https://fb.me/KnightsAndGlory
Twitter: https://twitter.com/glory_knights
